= SDL_IsTextInputActive =
Use this function to check whether or not Unicode text input events are enabled.




== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_bool SDL_IsTextInputActive(void)
```


== Return Value ==
Returns SDL_TRUE if text input events are enabled else SDL_FALSE.


